CHEESESTEAK showed no early speed, ran on to contend throughout with a mild bid too late. ZHU DADDY bothered from the gate, raced back with a bid far turn but faltered. VALERIE BLUE close up early on, raced along evenly from the half with no response from the far turn. AGENT KOSTA broke well, up close to the half, gave in readily. ENGLISH BOBBY bothered at the start and slow into stride with no bid thereafter fading far back. ROYALLY FLUSHED was through early and dropped well back. SWAYBACK JACK never factored throughout. Race was hand timed due to a bad sensor on the turf course, all turf races will be hand timed for the remainder of the meet. Acm
